MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

2003-1367. In re Application of Aboyade.

This cause came before the court upon the filing of a report in the Office of the Clerk of this court by the Board of Commissioners on Character and Fitness.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause be remanded to the Board of Commissioners on Character and Fitness to supplement its statement of facts and procedural background.
